Text: Thanks for the uploads, but is there a reason you've re-upped Hikaru, Love Hina, and Death Note less than a month after logros13 did? Are yours better quality?

I don't know if mine are of better quality than his.  I didn't even know that he uploaded them until after I uploaded mine.  While I can't be sure that they are of higher quality than logros13's, they could be, so it might be worth it to download to see if it is better or not.
